{"tid":294324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普稱將禁止新移民首五年享任何福利","createTime":"2017-06-23T01:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T20:07:54.000Z","uid":28435,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2b0b51de6d91085c37e3d214f9eabee3221722","tid":294324,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱將禁止新移民首五年享任何福利<br />\n<br />\n23.06.2017 08:56<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普透露，他將會推出新的移民法令，禁止新移民在首五年獲得任何福利。<br />\n<br />\n他說，這樣做是希望到美國的人，能夠經濟獨立。今次是特朗普首次表明有意削減新移民福利，但無透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又簽署新的行政命令，取消前奧巴馬政府加快辦理非移民簽證的規定，但白宮官員無解釋背後原因。"},{"pid":"67bb68cf2b038e6133f7c004bb3922509022a4e7","tid":294324,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:19:01.000Z","msg":"岩, 無錢學乜人移民"},{"pid":"d078d05508cdd52fbcf233b236a23d890bfe88e8","tid":294324,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:23:15.000Z","msg":"好唔仁道"},{"pid":"85572f8c5e06833baa4962edd565437aca923592","tid":294324,"uid":67903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"香港咁做都好<br />\n<br />\n可惜過唔到半票"},{"pid":"323ebef804446677be47dc0899130b419a245fe6","tid":294324,"uid":59641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"其實所有國家既移民政策都應該咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d12088677599a5ba248a565776acfe1212c2e7","tid":294324,"uid":3302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"唉 好希望香港有trump<br />\n簽行政命令殺哂班支那南亞豬"},{"pid":"35c329427775185158f5d15ca432b33ba5c5573e","tid":294324,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"根主就係應該要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d79e8f3a3f5c3ffe0737f9bd400c4cd2022df2","tid":294324,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blo